FORRT Contributor Analyses

Last updated on May 10, 2025

As of 26 June 2025, FORRT has a total of 89 completed or ongoing projects and support teams, with a total of 574 contributors. There is an average (mean) of 2.47 contributions per person across all FORRT projects, and the average number of contributors per project is 15.61. You can see the full list of FORRT contributors and their indivudual contributions here.
